HEADWORD: Forficula
<hw>For*fic"u*la</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L., small
shears, scissors, dim. of <ets>forfex</ets> shears.]</ety>
<fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A genus of insects including the earwigs. See
<er>Earwig</er>, 1.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

